ur own Cheddar at the beginning of the recipe, cut cheese in <nobr>2 cm<\/nobr> pieces and grate <nobr><strong>4-5 sec\/speed 8<\/strong>.<\/nobr> Transfer to a bowl and set aside then continue as per recipe.","For your next at-home movie night with the kids, try whipping up a batch of these cheesy nachos. A classic beef chilli bursting with mild Tex-Mex flavours is ladled over crunchy tortilla chips, topped with grated Cheddar then grilled until melted. Serve in bowls with sour cream and enjoy whilst watching a fun family blockbuster."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","40m","6 portions"]}